public class QueryResultPlanner
extends ContentPlanner

Plans the brief description of a resource that has been found through a query.

Version:
1.2 24-03-2008, 1.4 25-09-2008 This version plans a description of all matches that have been found, which the user can navigate in the same way as the browsing module.
